msgstr "Apple POST JWT"

#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
msgid "The Apple OIDC provider uses a `client_secret_post` method, in which the secret is a JWT produced with a `private_key_jwt` authentication method, but with the Apple account-specific issuer and subject claims."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
msgid "In Quarkus Security, `quarkus-oidc` supports a non-standard `client_secret_post_jwt` authentication method, which you can configure as follows:"
msgstr "Quarkus Security では、 `quarkus-oidc` が非標準の `client_secret_post_jwt` 認証方法をサポートしており、次のように設定できます。"

